{"tid":1039262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢仔船p!:)窮撚勿入!","createTime":"2019-02-27T09:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T10:27:24.000Z","uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4873d3e12db0203afd81e1c62924535cc5f761","tid":1039262,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。夜晚出海。<br />\n<br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻 Adela , 租的。<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://i56.tinypic.com/idwxuv.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi56.tinypic.com%2Fidwxuv.jpg&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=15644f00\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://i56.tinypic.com/idwxuv.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://i53.tinypic.com/2ldit53.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi53.tinypic.com%2F2ldit53.jpg&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=c3f42734\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://i53.tinypic.com/2ldit53.jpg</a><br />\n坐50人的，長80幾呎。<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的 Princess V62 坐20人 西班牙式遊艇<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://i54.tinypic.com/snf8zo.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi54.tinypic.com%2Fsnf8zo.png&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=3d8efc3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://i54.tinypic.com/snf8zo.png</a><br />\n<br />\n最後仲有一隻比較有中國古典風嘅小型浪漫情趣遊艇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJNrUR8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJNrUR8.png&h=be7b57d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男仔參加費每人2000<br />\n絲打免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18c68fd1d0240879f90cfb50cce024f2b47336f","tid":1039262,"uid":99568,"